Page background       → bg-[--bg-page]      or  bg-[#F8FAFC]
Card / modal          → bg-[--bg-card]      or  bg-white dark:bg-[#1E293B]
Sidebar / navbar      → bg-[--bg-sidebar]
Input field           → bg-[--bg-input]

Primary button        → bg-primary hover:bg-primary-hover text-white
Active nav link       → bg-primary-light text-primary
Selected chip         → bg-primary-light border-primary text-primary
Unselected chip       → bg-[--bg-input] border-[--border] text-[--text-muted]

Overdue badge         → bg-red-100 text-red-800       (light)
                        dark:bg-red-900 dark:text-red-200
Upcoming badge        → bg-amber-100 text-amber-800
Later badge           → bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800
Completed badge       → bg-slate-100 text-slate-500

Reminder badge        → bg-purple-light text-purple
Notification bell     → text-purple
Unread notif bg       → bg-purple-light dark:bg-purple/20

Body text             → text-[--text]
Label / desc text     → text-[--text-secondary]
Metadata / date       → text-[--text-muted]
Placeholder           → placeholder:text-[--text-placeholder]

Card border           → border border-[--border]
Divider line          → border-b border-[--border]


